What you need to know:

Odoyo, a former Kenyan international all-rounder, is a member of the organising committee of Dafabet Africa Premier League T20 cricket tournamentAccording to Odoyo, they had selected 100 players from different counties and some promising Under-19 players to beef up some of the participating teamsDafabet Africa Premier League T20 cricket tournament, which batted off on Thursday morning, had already unsettled the dust at Ruaraka Sports Club with four matches being played on Thursday and Friday